          module: []
          output: After several days in isolation, the cleric recovers his wits.
            It appears this episode was naught but a fleeting bout of madness. Having
            reflected upon his errors, the cleric is now prepared to return to his
            duties.
        - weight: 30
          module:
          - rid: 107151358184390663
          - rid: 107151358184390664
          output: 'We have a problem... the cleric has escaped his confinement. Reports
            are flooding in of a naked madman shrieking in the streets about the
            coming apocalypse and the righteous punishment of the Beholder. Lamentably,
            a rival sect has already identified him as one of our own.

            [Lost
            20 Zeal & 10 Bliss]

